name: BunnyHopes “santa”
description:
Bunny transformed to Santa, however in order to Father Christmas, he must also be fully-vaccinated. 
This year, Christmas present is a task for each and everyone of us to take care and safeguard the Nature, even though at the end it's only amounted to talks on social media or hastags. In this ruined planet, the Santa can't deliver his presents due to horrible air pollution causing his reindeers to be easily susceptible to diseases and unable to travel far... 😢
